item_name: Giovanna Collection Women's Irregular Stripe 3-pc Skirt Suit
product_description: Look chic and put together in this skirt suit from Giovanna Collection. This three-piece ensemble features an asymmetrical design to let you show your sense of style while remaining professional. Made from virtual silk fabric, all 3 parts are fully lined. The camisole has a side zipper closure for ease of wearing, the skirt has side elastic and back zipper closure. Complimentary brooch on jacket. Measurement taken from size 10: jacket length from center back = 25", camisole length = 23", skirt length = 30". Hats on model are NOT included.
